Ideoblothrus pisolitus

differs from all other species of the genus by the noticeably more slender pedipalpal patella and chela, which are 2.22–2.26 (
„
), 2.08–2.27 (
♀
) and chela (with pedicel) 3.36–3.47 (
„
), 3.07 (
♀
